ning body, the Pakistan Cricket Board, other sports and their associated bodies have been dogged by allegations of political appointments and embezzlement, infighting and a lack of funding.\", \"from\": 4490, \"to\": 4754, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4580, \"end\": 4602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Cricket_Board\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pakistan Cricket Board\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Cricket_Board\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_Cricket_Board\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"public and media focus\", \"from\": 4495, \"to\": 4517}, {\"ngram\": \"cricket\", \"from\": 4529, \"to\": 4536}, {\"ngram\": \"the richest governing body\", \"from\": 4548, \"to\": 4574}, {\"ngram\": \"other sports\", \"from\": 4604, \"to\": 4616}, {\"ngram\": \"their associated bodies\", \"from\": 4621, \"to\": 4644}, {\"ngram\": \"allegations\", \"from\": 4665, \"to\": 4676}, {\"ngram\": \"political appointments\", \"from\": 4680, \"to\": 4702}, {\"ngram\": \"embezzlement\", \"from\": 4707, \"to\": 4719}, {\"ngram\": \"infighting\", \"from\": 4721, \"to\": 4731}, {\"ngram\": \"a lack\", \"from\": 4736, \"to\": 4742}, {\"ngram\": \"funding\", \"from\": 4746, \"to\": 4753}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes have relied on public and private organisations, such as banks, to set up sports departments that would provide an income stream and a career pathway, but with the country's economic downturn in the past few years, many have closed their sports departments.\", \"from\": 4756, \"to\": 5022, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athletes\", \"from\": 4756, \"to\": 4764}, {\"ngram\": \"public and private organisations\", \"from\": 4780, \"to\": 4812}, {\"ngram\": \"banks\", \"from\": 4822, \"to\": 4827}, {\"ngram\": \"sports departments\", \"from\": 4839, \"to\": 4857}, {\"ngram\": \"an income stream\", \"from\": 4877, \"to\": 4893}, {\"ngram\": \"a career pathway\", \"from\": 